    "text":  "<b>Sorting Defined Help</b><br /><br />Answering Questions<ol><li><b>Read</b> the directions at the start of the activity.</li><li>Then, read each question and answer choice.</li><li>Use the <b>speaker button</b> to listen to the recorded audio when available.</li><li>Click or tap your answer, and don't let go! Then, drag it to the response line.</li><li>As an alternative to the mouse, the keyboard may be used. Tab to your answer, press Space to select it, and press Enter to place it on the response line.</li><li>Use the <b>Check</b> button to find out if your answer is correct.</li><li>If the answer is incorrect, use the <b>Try Again button</b>, then choose a new answer.</li><li>Use the <b>Previous</b> and <b>Next</b> buttons to navigate between question screens. You may review previous answers. </li></ol>Top Buttons<ol><li>Use the button with the <b>question mark</b> to come back to this help page.</li><li>Use the button with the <b>X</b> to close the activity.</li><li>Use the button with the <b>speaker</b> to mute automatic audio feedback.</li></ol>",
